    {"prompt": "Sonoluminescence — collapse a tiny bubble with sound waves and it briefly reaches temperatures hotter than the sun's surface, emitting a flash of light. A single bubble in water, pulsed by ultrasound, produces picosecond flashes. Animate the bubble dynamics and the mystery of the mechanism.", "category": "physics_phenomena"},
