    {"prompt": "Bose-Einstein Condensation — cool atoms to near absolute zero and they all collapse into the same quantum state, behaving as one giant 'super-atom.' Animate the velocity distribution narrowing as temperature drops, and show the matter wave coherence.", "category": "physics_phenomena"},
